## Third-Party Acknowledgments

This project builds upon and includes concepts from:

### Original SSD1306_OLED_json Project
- Original Author: yishunzhikong
- Repository: https://github.com/yishunzhikong/SSD1306_OLED_json
- License: [Original project license]
- Contributions: JSON configuration system, basic OLED display functionality

### Extended SSD1306_OLED_json Fork
- Author: bearcatl  
- Repository: https://github.com/bearcatl/SSD1306_OLED_json
- License: [Fork project license]
- Contributions: Extended functionality and system monitoring features

### cJSON Library
- Author: Dave Gamble and cJSON contributors
- Repository: https://github.com/DaveGamble/cJSON
- License: MIT License
- Usage: JSON parsing and generation

### I2C Communication Libraries
- Various contributors to Linux I2C subsystem
- Usage: Hardware communication with OLED displays

